author: AccessWDUN Staff
title: Volleyball: Jefferson finishes second in 8-AAA
text: White County could not hold a 14-point lead as Stephens County rallied in the second half to take a 21-20 win over the Warriors Friday night in Region 8-AAAA action at White County Stadium. 8:52AM ( 16 hours ago ) The Jefferson defense held Morgan County to just 136 total yards and pitched its second shutout of the season Friday night in a 17-0 win at Memorial Stadium. 8:30AM ( 16 hours ago ) Fannin County's offense stormed out of the gates and helped the Rebels pull out a 41-35 win over Lumpkin County on Friday in Dahlonega. 8:16AM ( 16 hours ago )
